<br>
<strong>IN&#45;TEXT CITATION</strong>
<br>
<br>
When referring to an artwork in your writing, it may be useful to include the title as well as the 
author&#8217;s name. (Note: when referring to a whole work, page numbers are not needed).
<br>
<br>
<blockquote class="in-text-citation">
	In <em>Kitchen Sink Daydreams</em>, Smith conveys a sense of heightened emotion&hellip;
</blockquote>
